abstract: ATLANTIC CITY, Aug. 8 (UPI) Sun Tumble rallied from sixth place with a quartermile to go today to gain a 1 length victory in the feature race as the season started at the Atlantic City Race Course.

abstract: Miss Leonore Judith Stern, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Richard H. Stern of 150 East 61st Street, was married last evening to Robert Neil Snyder, son of Mr. and Mrs. Murray Snyder of Forest Hills, Queens. Rabbi Bernard Bamberger performed the ceremony at the St. RegisSheraton Roof.

abstract: LITCHFIELD, Conn., Aug. 6 Bob Russell piloted Right Solution, a 6-year-old brown gelding, to the open working hunter championship today at the Litchfield horse show.
